Hillsbori

June 4, 1935 Merle J. Pratt v. Hazel M. Magnuson & a. Frederick J. Gaffney, for the plaintiff, furnished no brief. Osgood & Osgood and 0. Neil Tolman, for the defendants, furnished no brief. Per Curiam.

The defendants were entitled to the order granting the motion as matter of law. Farnum v. Company, 69 N. H. 231.

Exception overruled.
